easymvp.usecase

Class ObservableUseCase<R,Q>

  • java.lang.Object
    • easymvp.usecase.UseCase<rx.Observable,Q>
      • easymvp.usecase.ObservableUseCase<R,Q>
  • Type Parameters:
    R - The response value emitted by the Observable.
    Q - The request value.

    public abstract class ObservableUseCase<R,Q>
extends UseCase<rx.Observable,Q>
    Reactive version of a UseCase.

    The presenter simply subscribes to Observable returned by the execute(Object) method.
